body.text:
I believe as long as hindi po siya detrimental to your health & your baby's health pwede po. Seek advice from your doctor as well. Also weigh if kakayanin mo ba physically and mentally especially sa time ng exams or kasagsagan ng maraming school tasks. Better to consult your insti head regarding this matter. 

I have friends who enrolled while pregnant (tho nasa ibang school pa ako nito & hindi ata aware ang school about their pregnancy), kaya naman nila tho sometimes pregnancy sickness gets in the way so it was hard for them to focus or sometimes stay awake in class. 

Goodluck anon! Stay safe and healthy! 🫶🏻

body.text: Hi Anon, I was pregnant last sem, and I took my summer term kahit medyo malaki na yung tyan ko. 😊 Idk, if halata ba ng guards or students that time, pero nakakapasok ako and bago ako pumasok and nag enroll, ininform ko yung head ng institute ko about my case. Pinayagan naman nila ako, pero ayun, hindi ka nila pipilitin na mag enroll as long as kaya mo, for the sake of the child. 😊
